 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/1668097753?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>从东翼看到的景色</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/1668222884?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9781668222881.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;从东翼看吉尔·拜登&lt;br /&gt;这位前第一夫人讲述了她在白宫的时光、她所倡导的事业以及她同时担任社区大学教授的工作。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 23:29:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/1668222884?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>革命</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/1631440888?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9781631440885.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;埃里克·梅塔克萨斯的《革命》&lt;br /&gt; 《马丁·路德》和《朋霍费尔》的作者讲述了美利坚合众国的建立。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 23:29:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/1631440888?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>修复方法</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/1644215551?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9781644215555.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;芭芭拉·麦克奎德的《修复》&lt;br /&gt;这位密歇根东区前美国检察官描述了她认为对美国民主和国家安全的威胁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 23:29:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/1644215551?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>美国的抵抗史</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/158642436X?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9781586424367.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;《美国的抵抗史》作者：Tad Stoermer&lt;br /&gt;美国历史上阐明抵抗与权力之间紧张关系的时刻。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 23:29:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.amazon.com/dp/158642436X?tag=thenewyorktim-20</guid></item><item><title>导师的残骸</title><link>https://www.amazon.com/dp/1324096322?tag=thenewyorktim-20</link><description>&lt;img src="https://static01.nyt.com/bestsellers/images/9781324096320.jpg" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;《导师的残骸》埃里克·杰·